## Resolved mutable: edge-case-lock-race-windows

gm-plugkit/plugkit-wasm-wrapper.js:2674-2683 acquireLock() has TOCTOU window: checkExistingHolder() reads content+pid at T1, unlinks at T2. Between T1 and T2, holder can crash, and concurrent agent can slip through. fs.openSync with 'wx' is atomic but unlink is not guarded.